            "title": "摩根士丹利因AI基建需求將諾基亞列為首選股",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"摩根士丹利因AI基建需求將諾基亞列為首選股\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ac23_7nto76G2n0gPA0QrQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/5da6e900-1e51-11f1-afdb-6b8271a9ff69\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">摩根士丹利因AI基建需求將諾基亞列為首選股</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
